101
00:09:13,510 --> 00:09:15,580
See?

102
00:09:15,580 --> 00:09:18,450
Cut the nonsense and tell me honestly.

103
00:09:18,450 --> 00:09:20,670
There was someone else here. Right?

104
00:09:20,670 --> 00:09:23,910
Is he someone close to Yook Dong Joo?

105
00:09:23,910 --> 00:09:26,500
Did you get threatened by that person?

106
00:09:27,330 --> 00:09:30,370
