00:12:57,040 --> 00:13:00,220
It'll take forever to clean all this up.

149
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:03,760
When's the writer coming?

150
00:13:05,130 --> 00:13:07,380
- I don't know. 
 - Where did he go?

151
00:13:07,380 --> 00:13:09,630
He didn't tell me.

152
00:13:19,130 --> 00:13:21,480
Hey, did you find it?

153
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:24,010
Okay, I'll be on my way.

