00:17:18,270 --> 00:17:21,260
How dare you yell like that?

208
00:17:21,260 --> 00:17:24,180
G-Gosh, I-I'm sorry.

209
00:17:24,180 --> 00:17:27,100
So, you have no fear now that you've become a bit famous?

210
00:17:27,100 --> 00:17:30,000
No, that's not it. I-I just got worked up.

211
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:34,100
Kang San had a close friend.

212
00:17:36,250 --> 00:17:38,910
He's working as a teacher here.

213
00:17:38,910 --> 00:17:40,760
So go meet him.

214
00:17:46,050 --> 00:17:47,830
 How many times do I have to tell you? 

215
00:17:47,830 --> 00:17:50,650
 Hyung didn't run away from home. There's no reason. 

216
00:17:50,650 --> 00:17:52,720
 Something must've happened to him. 

