00:17:58,910 --> 00:18:01,830
 - So what do you want me to do? 
 - You need to find him! 

220
00:18:01,830 --> 00:18:04,290
 The police shouldn't be sitting around like this. 

221
00:18:04,290 --> 00:18:09,400
 Gosh, even a fucking brat is giving me bullshit. 

222
00:18:09,400 --> 00:18:11,600
 How dare you glare at me like that? 

223
00:18:11,600 --> 00:18:13,870
 The police shouldn't be like this. 

224
00:18:13,870 --> 00:18:15,560
 The police need to find him! 

225
00:18:15,560 --> 00:18:18,850
 Where will we find a fucking orphan who ran off on his own two feet? 

226
00:18:18,850 --> 00:18:20,760
 You can go find him if you want! 

227
00:18:20,760 --> 00:18:24,890
 Do orphans... not deserve to be protected by the police? 

228
00:18:24,890 --> 00:18:27,430
 If you don't have parents, we're not citizens of this country? 

229
00:18:27,430 --> 00:18:29,740
 This fucking asshole! 

230
00:18:33,620 --> 00:18:36,090
 You sure make it obvious how uneducated you are. 

231
00:18:36,090 --> 00:18:37,160
 Leave. 

232
00:18:37,160 --> 00:18:39,550
 - I'm telling you to do your job as the police! 
 - What? 

233
00:18:39,550 --> 00:18:42,600
 - This fucking bastard— 
 - Stop cursing! 

234
00:18:43,320 --> 00:18:45,440
 I'm not your fucking son. 

235
00:18:45,440 --> 00:18:48,180
 You didn't even bother trying to look for my brother. 

236
00:18:48,180 --> 00:18:50,520
 You never intended so in the first place! 

237
00:18:50,520 --> 00:18:53,170
 - Do your job as the police! 
 - Come outside! 

238
00:18:53,170 --> 00:18:55,700
 Let go! Let go of me! 

239
00:18:55,700 --> 00:18:58,900
 - He's not a runaway! 
 - Kang San! 

240
00:18:59,760 --> 00:19:01,590
That was...

241
00:19:02,390 --> 00:19:05,340
the last time I saw Kang San.

242
00:19:05,970 --> 00:19:10,960
Was there anything odd about Lee Kang San, by chance?

243
00:19:10,960 --> 00:19:13,950
Do you think Lee Kang San is your friend?

244
00:19:13,950 --> 00:19:15,840
